This paper deals with the problem of human-robot interaction and learning from human behavior. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the importance of effective communication between the human and the robot, which falls under the category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper presents proof-of-concept experiments, which could fall under the category of cs.SI (Systems and Control).
